<div class="bmi-card-aka">Lipid Panel</div>
<div class="bmi-card-desc">A proxy for cardiovascular risk; best interpreted alongside ApoB and particle size for a complete picture.</div>
<div class="bmi-card-footer">
<span class="bmi-card-optimal">LDL optimal: &lt; 70 mg/dL</span>
<span class="bmi-card-arrow">&#8594;</span>
</div>
</a>

<a href="/biomarkers/triglycerides" class="bmi-card available">
<div class="bmi-card-name">Triglycerides</div>
<div class="bmi-card-aka">Serum Triglycerides</div>
<div class="bmi-card-desc">Reflects carbohydrate metabolism and visceral fat load. Elevated levels are strongly modulated by diet and exercise.</div>
<div class="bmi-card-footer">
<span class="bmi-card-optimal">Optimal: &lt; 80 mg/dL</span>
<span class="bmi-card-arrow">&#8594;</span>
</div>
</a>

