<div class="bmi-card-desc">Genetically determined cardiovascular risk factor — largely unaffected by lifestyle. Critical to know, even if hard to modify.</div>
<div class="bmi-card-footer">
<span class="bmi-card-optimal">Optimal: &lt; 30 mg/dL</span>
<span class="bmi-card-arrow">&#8594;</span>
</div>
</a>

<a href="/biomarkers/homocysteine" class="bmi-card available">
<div class="bmi-card-name">Homocysteine</div>
<div class="bmi-card-aka">Total Homocysteine</div>
<div class="bmi-card-desc">Elevated levels damage arterial walls and raise dementia risk. Often correctable with B-vitamin supplementation.</div>
<div class="bmi-card-footer">
<span class="bmi-card-optimal">Optimal: &lt; 7 µmol/L</span>
<span class="bmi-card-arrow">&#8594;</span>
</div>
</a>

